{"tid":2177607,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞士與中國擬續簽不道德協議　允許中國公安入境追蹤中國公民","createTime":"2020-08-28T00:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T01:41:04.000Z","uid":18569,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"84c7d7c8e5e34ec8ad6e125dbe8fc7451e51732f","tid":2177607,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T00:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gfmSwaS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgfmSwaS.jpg&h=c13dbd52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n瑞士媒體《新蘇黎世報》周日（23日）報道，瑞士聯邦政府正與中國商談續簽一項秘密協議，允許中國官員可以進入瑞士，追蹤在瑞士「非法」滯留的中國公民。<br />\n<br />\n《新蘇黎世報》指，香港已強行實施《國安法》，在瑞士的香港民主人士可能遭逮捕； 當地的維吾爾人亦可能會遭鎮壓。<br />\n<br />\n世維會發言人迪里夏提（Dilxat Raxit）向本台表示，中共對維吾爾人實施「種族滅絕政策」，擔心協議會令在瑞士生活的很多維吾爾人被中共國安人員跟蹤，並利用獲取的信息迫害他們及在境內的家人。有關問題甚至可能導致當地的維吾爾人、藏人甚至港人身陷險境。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">瑞士外長卡西斯（Ignazio Cassis）本月初曾罕見表態，稱中國已背離改革之路且嚴重侵犯人權，瑞士對此不會坐視不理，他還關切了香港《國安法》的實施。其表態收穫國際讚譽。但該秘密協議令瑞士人權形象急跌。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/sweden-deal-08262020081313.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fsweden-deal-08262020081313.html&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONqNFN85aI5NoQ2W41nR4Hcs%3D&h=81ae3d4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/sweden-deal-08262020081313.html</a>"},{"pid":"5763c20217a3e211d3d7368ce04b5b97a1ce4ba5","tid":2177607,"uid":243677,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T00:12:41.000Z","msg":"維尼睇死班歐洲佬會奶 所以先照係香港推國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 